01:41:29,160 --> 01:41:33,370
You're still awake. - No. I am scared.

1608
01:41:35,160 --> 01:41:38,370
Feels like something is not right.

1609
01:41:38,870 --> 01:41:41,870
You look.. - Me?

1610
01:41:44,370 --> 01:41:45,370
What, Riya?

1611
01:41:45,410 --> 01:41:49,250
Just tell me that what I'm thinking is wrong.

1612
01:41:50,120 --> 01:41:52,120
Just tell me it's my imagination.

1613
01:41:52,540 --> 01:41:54,370
Just tell me it'll all be fine, Adi.

1614
01:41:54,500 --> 01:41:57,620
Just..just tell me that you love me.

1615
01:41:57,660 --> 01:42:00,250
Just that..

1616
01:42:00,620 --> 01:42:02,660
Please.. - Adi, tell me.

1617
01:42:02,750 --> 01:42:04,870
Adi. - Please calm down.

1618
01:42:22,040 --> 01:42:25,410
I am sorry. I am really sorry, Riya.

1619
01:42:26,120 --> 01:42:27,750
I am tired.

1620
01:42:29,290 --> 01:42:30,870
Go get some sleep.

1621
01:42:32,000 --> 01:42:33,370
I need some rest.

1622
01:42:46,160 --> 01:42:47,250
Good night.

1623
01:43:00,120 --> 01:43:01,000
Excuse me. - Yes, ma'am.

1624
01:43:01,120 --> 01:43:03,250
I said satin curtains in this section.

1625
01:43:03,540 --> 01:43:04,910
These are not satin.

1626
01:43:05,500 --> 01:43:08,040
Okay, rosewater, welcome drink and..

1627
01:43:08,120 --> 01:43:10,870
And these flowers? - Ma'am, you said white flowers.

1628
01:43:10,910 --> 01:43:12,870
I said white orchids.

1629
01:43:13,160 --> 01:43:14,660
Riya. - What?

1630
01:43:15,500 --> 01:43:16,370
What are you doing?

1631
01:43:16,500 --> 01:43:18,750
Forget all this, and get ready.

1632
01:43:19,160 --> 01:43:20,620
How can I?

1633
01:43:20,750 --> 01:43:23,750
I specifically said I don't want florescent color.

1634
01:43:23,790 --> 01:43:25,160
I just want soothing colors. - That's okay.

1635
01:43:25,290 --> 01:43:26,870
Relax, dear. It will all be fine.

1636
01:43:27,000 --> 01:43:29,370
When will it be fine, dad? After my marriage.

1637
01:43:30,370 --> 01:43:31,870
Everything's wrong here.

1638
01:43:32,000 --> 01:43:33,910
Everything's wrong in my marriage.

1639
01:43:34,910 --> 01:43:37,790
Dad, everything is going wrong in my marriage.

1640
01:43:39,040 --> 01:43:41,870
Nothing, nothing, nothing will go wrong in your marriage.

1641
01:43:41,910 --> 01:43:42,870
I am right here.

1642
01:43:43,000 --> 01:43:45,120
Look at me. Nothing will go wrong.

1643
01:43:45,250 --> 01:43:48,000
I will make sure everything goes right.

1644
01:43:48,410 --> 01:43:50,160
Oh my..what kind of a place is this?

1645
01:43:50,410 --> 01:43:51,870
You can't find a single thing.

1646
01:43:52,370 --> 01:43:53,870
Back in India, you make one call..

1647
01:43:54,000 --> 01:43:55,790
..and the shopkeeper delivers the goods to your doorstep.

1648
01:43:55,870 --> 01:43:58,250
Here's the telephone.

1649
01:43:58,290 --> 01:44:01,870
Call room service and tell them what to get.

1650
01:44:02,040 --> 01:44:06,160
I see..I can't find the drawstring of your pajamas.

1651
01:44:06,250 --> 01:44:08,250
Call room service and ask them to get it.

1652
01:44:09,410 --> 01:44:10,750
Hello, drawstring..

1653
01:44:11,120 --> 01:44:12,410
You don't get drawstrings here.

1654
01:44:12,500 --> 01:44:14,620
Exactly, I can't find anything.

1655
01:44:14,870 --> 01:44:17,790
And since the time you got here, you've been behaving like a tourist.

1656
01:44:17,870 --> 01:44:20,120
As if only my son's getting married.

1657
01:44:21,120 --> 01:44:22,370
And son..

1658
01:44:22,540 --> 01:44:25,000
Why are you so upset?

1659
01:44:25,160 --> 01:44:25,870
It's not good.

1660
01:44:25,910 --> 01:44:27,660
Now go get ready quickly.

1661
01:44:27,790 --> 01:44:29,160
You.. - And listen.

1662
01:44:31,370 --> 01:44:32,250
Listen..

1663
01:44:32,540 --> 01:44:36,000
The list which the priest gave us also has betel leaves.

1664
01:44:36,250 --> 01:44:38,250
They should be here by the nuptial rounds.

1665
01:44:38,370 --> 01:44:40,910
Oh Lord..what is this you gave me?

1666
01:44:42,790 --> 01:44:47,120
I can't believe this is the same woman I married.

1667
01:44:47,500 --> 01:44:51,910
If I am lying for a minute, it makes her mad.

1668
01:44:54,160 --> 01:44:55,290
Crazy woman.

1669
01:45:05,000 --> 01:45:07,540
What are you up to?

1670
01:45:11,660 --> 01:45:12,910
Adi..

1671
01:45:14,870 --> 01:45:19,250
Don't think I don't know what's going on in your life.

1672
01:45:19,910 --> 01:45:21,370
I know it all.

1673
01:45:23,040 --> 01:45:24,290
I am your father.

1674
01:45:27,290 --> 01:45:30,540
Seriousness doesn't look good on my face.

1675
01:45:31,870 --> 01:45:33,500
But all I would say..

1676
01:45:34,790 --> 01:45:38,620
..do what your heart says.

1677
01:45:43,120 --> 01:45:44,000
My son.

1678
01:45:51,750 --> 01:45:54,620
There's no place for dreams in reality, Anushka.

1679
01:45:56,540 --> 01:45:57,750
Get ready quickly.

1680
01:45:57,790 --> 01:45:59,160
Jay's waiting for you.

1681
01:46:04,120 --> 01:46:05,870
Just excuse us, please.

1682
01:46:06,120 --> 01:46:07,410
I'll be right back, Anushka.

1683
01:46:10,370 --> 01:46:14,540
Anushka, I invited you and your family over..

1684
01:46:14,620 --> 01:46:16,540
..and gave them a lot of respect.

1685
01:46:16,620 --> 01:46:18,000
Would you agree?

1686
01:46:18,500 --> 01:46:19,370
Yeah!

1687
01:46:19,660 --> 01:46:21,620
So isn't it your duty to..

1688
01:46:21,660 --> 01:46:24,500
..to think about Adi and my family's respect?

1689
01:46:25,620 --> 01:46:28,410
Uncle, I didn't understand.

1690
01:46:29,040 --> 01:46:29,910
What are you trying to say?

1691
01:46:30,000 --> 01:46:31,870
Alright. I'll be direct.

1692
01:46:32,410 --> 01:46:35,290
Adi isn't just getting Riya's love from this marriage.

1693
01:46:35,750 --> 01:46:39,500
He's getting a opportunity to fulfill all the dreams that he saw.

1694
01:46:40,370 --> 01:46:41,750
I know.

1695
01:46:42,410 --> 01:46:45,000
Who would know about Adi's dreams better than me?

1696
01:46:46,540 --> 01:46:47,910
But you don't know that..

1697
01:46:48,000 --> 01:46:50,790
..there's a thin line between friendship and love.

1698
01:46:51,660 --> 01:46:53,500
And it's hard to say when you cross it.

1699
01:46:53,870 --> 01:46:57,250
The friendship that you and Adi share..

1700
01:46:57,620 --> 01:46:59,660
..keep it till that.

1701
01:47:00,000 --> 01:47:01,040
You got that?

1702
01:47:01,250 --> 01:47:03,910
Because only Riya has a right to Adi's love.

1703
01:47:05,370 --> 01:47:08,500
And love is for the one that has the right to it.

1704
01:47:09,040 --> 01:47:12,660
I hope I've made myself..amply clear.

1705
01:47:15,620 --> 01:47:16,910
Yes.

1706
01:47:18,910 --> 01:47:20,410
Yes.

1707
01:47:22,250 --> 01:47:25,410
Uncle, you made everything very clear.

1708
01:47:26,910 --> 01:47:28,410
You are right.

1709
01:47:30,870 --> 01:47:36,370
And love is for the one that has the right to it.

1710
01:47:37,660 --> 01:47:38,870
Yes.

1711
01:47:39,250 --> 01:47:40,370
Good!

1712
01:47:52,500 --> 01:47:54,660
I said I'm not in the mood to talk.

1713
01:47:54,910 --> 01:47:57,000
By the time you're in the mood to talk..

1714
01:47:57,040 --> 01:47:59,120
..it will be worthless.

1715
01:47:59,540 --> 01:48:02,750
Why are you yelling? - So that I knock some sense in you.

1716
01:48:02,910 --> 01:48:04,160
Forget it, Petha.

1717
01:48:04,540 --> 01:48:07,660
He can't see what everyone can.

1718
01:48:08,250 --> 01:48:10,120
So how can he hear your voice?

1719
01:48:10,250 --> 01:48:11,870
Have you two lost your mind?

1720
01:48:12,370 --> 01:48:14,660
Stop yelling at me and go get booze. - Booze?

1721
01:48:14,910 --> 01:48:18,040
Should we drink on the occasion of your marriage..

1722
01:48:18,120 --> 01:48:19,370
..or to drown your sorrows?

1723
01:48:20,120 --> 01:48:23,000
Mind your tongue. You're talking about my marriage.

1724
01:48:23,040 --> 01:48:24,660
You're not the only one getting married.

1725
01:48:24,750 --> 01:48:26,000
Anushka's getting married too.

1726
01:48:26,120 --> 01:48:28,500
And whether you think about her or not, but we do.

1727
01:48:29,500 --> 01:48:31,370
What do you mean by I don't think about her?

1728
01:48:31,540 --> 01:48:32,250
You do?

1729
01:48:32,370 --> 01:48:34,750
Then go tell Riya that you don't love her.

1730
01:48:34,790 --> 01:48:36,290
You love Anushka. Tell her.

1731
01:48:39,620 --> 01:48:43,250
Forget it, Petha. It's not his cup of tea,

1732
01:48:43,410 --> 01:48:44,620
He's a coward.

1733
01:48:44,660 --> 01:48:47,000
Who are you to tell me?

1734
01:48:47,620 --> 01:48:48,620
It's my life. - Leave.

1735
01:48:48,750 --> 01:48:50,500
No! It's not just your life.

1736
01:48:50,540 --> 01:48:51,790
Leave him. - Understood.

1737
01:48:51,870 --> 01:48:57,250
You're ruining Anushka, Riya as well as Jay's life too.

1738
01:48:57,370 --> 01:49:01,410
Seems like you love your bike more than their lives.

1739
01:49:01,500 --> 01:49:03,120
Leave him.

1740
01:49:04,620 --> 01:49:06,040
There's no point talking to him.

1741
01:49:06,370 --> 01:49:07,410
Let's go. Come on.

1742
01:49:08,040 --> 01:49:10,290
You do what you want. Come on.

1743
01:49:17,370 --> 01:49:20,000
Take the bride's hand in yours.

1744
01:49:20,160 --> 01:49:25,250
I am in love..what to do?

1745
01:49:28,250 --> 01:49:29,750
Sprinkle water.

1746
01:49:30,410 --> 01:49:37,250
I am in love..what to do?

1747
01:49:37,370 --> 01:49:41,750
I am in love..what to do?

1748
01:49:41,790 --> 01:49:43,910
Now pour clarified butter in the fire.

1749
01:49:44,120 --> 01:49:50,500
I can't live..or die.

1750
01:49:51,790 --> 01:49:53,000
Adi. - Yeah.

1751
01:49:53,290 --> 01:49:55,870
The priest is asking us to pour clarified butter in the fire. - Yes.

1752
01:49:57,790 --> 01:50:04,540
I am in love..what to do?

1753
01:50:04,750 --> 01:50:08,910
I am in love..what to do?

1754
01:50:09,000 --> 01:50:11,370
Adi, where are you lost?

1755
01:50:11,870 --> 01:50:14,120
Petha, Nikki, Batli..I don't see anyone.

1756
01:50:17,500 --> 01:50:19,250
Adi, we're getting married.

1757
01:50:20,160 --> 01:50:22,790
And you're still thinking about your friends.

1758
01:50:35,370 --> 01:50:36,750
Where are granny and Gulabo?

1759
01:50:42,790 --> 01:50:43,620
Adi?

1760
01:50:44,540 --> 01:50:45,660
Adi?

1761
01:50:49,370 --> 01:50:50,370
Where is everyone?

1762
01:50:50,500 --> 01:50:52,290
Petha, where's Anushka?

1763
01:50:52,500 --> 01:50:53,620
Where's Anushka?

1764
01:50:53,870 --> 01:50:54,870
She left.

1765
01:50:55,660 --> 01:50:57,370
She went back to London.

1766
01:51:02,620 --> 01:51:05,620
Adi, we're getting married.

1767
01:51:06,370 --> 01:51:08,290
You're still thinking about Anushka.

1768
01:51:08,370 --> 01:51:11,620
Anushka's gone. - Yes, she left.

1769
01:51:11,910 --> 01:51:14,750
Because she can't watch you marrying me.

1770
01:51:14,790 --> 01:51:17,290
She loves you. - I love her too!

1771
01:51:19,750 --> 01:51:20,660
Move aside.

1772
01:51:21,290 --> 01:51:22,500
I love her.

1773
01:51:23,750 --> 01:51:24,910
How dare you?

1774
01:51:25,500 --> 01:51:26,750
Hold on!

1775
01:51:28,910 --> 01:51:32,620
Mr. Kumar, we can retaliate with violence as well.

1776
01:51:34,120 --> 01:51:36,790
But we can't solve this problem with hitting each other.

1777
01:51:36,910 --> 01:51:39,370
Because this matter concerns the heart..

1778
01:51:39,620 --> 01:51:41,370
..and I think it's beyond your understanding.

1779
01:51:41,910 --> 01:51:43,120
Let him hit me, papa.

1780
01:51:45,540 --> 01:51:47,250
But even though you hit me..

1781
01:51:49,250 --> 01:51:50,790
..I will be honest with you.

1782
01:51:52,250 --> 01:51:56,370
The truth..that took me really long to understand.

1783
01:51:58,540 --> 01:52:00,750
That I love Anushka.

1784
01:52:00,750 --> 01:52:02,500
Why you.. - Papa, please!

1785
01:52:03,500 --> 01:52:04,540
What?

1786
01:52:05,870 --> 01:52:08,290
Even I realized this truth.

1787
01:52:09,660 --> 01:52:12,750
My heart knew that he loved Anushka.

1788
01:52:14,290 --> 01:52:17,750
But maybe I took too long to realize this truth.

1789
01:52:18,000 --> 01:52:20,250
But how the hell can he do this?

1790
01:52:20,540 --> 01:52:21,910
You once said..

1791
01:52:23,370 --> 01:52:25,620
Even if you stop holding hands, relationships don't break.

1792
01:52:33,000 --> 01:52:34,500
Pardon me, Mr. Kumar.

1793
01:52:37,410 --> 01:52:40,250
I know this is your personal matter.

1794
01:52:42,370 --> 01:52:46,370
But when few lives are at the stake of ruination..

1795
01:52:47,120 --> 01:52:48,370
..then I can't keep quiet.

1796
01:52:49,500 --> 01:52:51,620
What do you want to say?

1797
01:52:52,290 --> 01:52:53,370
Just think, sir.

1798
01:52:54,750 --> 01:52:56,500
When will your daughter be happier?

1799
01:52:58,120 --> 01:53:00,500
If Adi doesn't marry Riya..

1800
01:53:01,040 --> 01:53:06,370
..or if Adi marries Riya, but keeps loving Anushka in his heart?

1801
01:53:08,660 --> 01:53:10,870
Everyone falls in love, Mr. Kumar.

1802
01:53:11,540 --> 01:53:14,910
But only a few have the courage to get their love.

1803
01:53:16,620 --> 01:53:19,120
Today Adi told the truth in front of everyone.

1804
01:53:19,750 --> 01:53:23,370
But somewhere everyone's betterment lies in his truth.

1805
01:53:27,160 --> 01:53:29,000
The rest is up to you to decide, sir.

1806
01:53:31,790 --> 01:53:33,500
Mr. Kapoor is right, papa.

1807
01:53:33,790 --> 01:53:36,120
Even if you get me married to Adi.

1808
01:53:37,540 --> 01:53:41,000
He won't be happy neither will I.

1809
01:53:42,750 --> 01:53:45,120
Because he loves Anushka.

1810
01:53:46,120 --> 01:53:47,870
I am really sorry, Riya.

1811
01:53:55,660 --> 01:53:56,620
Thank you, sir.

1812
01:54:47,160 --> 01:54:49,120
Anushka!

1813
01:55:04,370 --> 01:55:06,290
Anushka!

1814
01:55:17,410 --> 01:55:19,910
Adi! Adi!

1815
01:55:28,500 --> 01:55:29,660
Anushka!

1816
01:55:35,790 --> 01:55:41,870
I am still wondering..what just happened.

1817
01:55:42,620 --> 01:55:47,870
Everything feels new.

1818
01:55:48,000 --> 01:55:52,040
O beloved..

1819
01:55:53,040 --> 01:55:55,370
How? How can you leave me?

1820
01:55:55,500 --> 01:55:57,040
What else could I do, Adi?

1821
01:55:58,120 --> 01:56:00,870
Throw flowers at your marriage with Riya?

1822
01:56:02,620 --> 01:56:04,790
I thought you left me.

1823
01:56:06,410 --> 01:56:08,040
I almost died.

1824
01:56:08,870 --> 01:56:10,160
I love you, Adi.

1825
01:56:11,000 --> 01:56:11,750
I love you more.

1826
01:56:11,910 --> 01:56:20,120
O beloved..what is this condition?

1827
01:56:20,410 --> 01:56:23,750
Feels like love.

1828
01:56:23,910 --> 01:56:27,790
What have you done to me?

1829
01:56:28,910 --> 01:56:31,120
You knew that I would come.

1830
01:56:31,160 --> 01:56:33,370
Yes, I did.

1831
01:56:34,290 --> 01:56:35,290
Me too.

1832
01:56:36,910 --> 01:56:39,870
Jay. I am sorry, buddy.

1833
01:56:39,910 --> 01:56:42,500
There's no justification for love.

1834
01:56:44,000 --> 01:56:45,750
Love is just..love.

1835
01:56:46,370 --> 01:56:47,250
Thanks, Jay.

1836
01:56:47,500 --> 01:56:50,120
And by the way, I've booked your honeymoon tickets.

1837
01:56:58,750 --> 01:57:00,620
Adi..don't you think..

1838
01:57:00,660 --> 01:57:03,370
..we should get married before the honeymoon.

1839
01:57:05,620 --> 01:57:06,620
Yes!

1840
01:57:11,500 --> 01:57:13,620
Lambu, come down.

1841
01:57:14,000 --> 01:57:15,290
Come down.

1842
01:57:23,620 --> 01:57:27,250
Decorate the venue. Eat some sweets.

1843
01:57:27,290 --> 01:57:30,540
Shake a leg with the guests.

1844
01:57:31,410 --> 01:57:35,370
Anushka's married, now I can drink in peace.

1845
01:57:35,540 --> 01:57:38,160
Invite all your guests.

1846
01:57:39,000 --> 01:57:42,870
That Luv Kapoor's looking so hot.

1847
01:57:42,910 --> 01:57:44,410
I am looking hot.

1848
01:57:45,040 --> 01:57:48,500
The Wedding Pulav.

1849
01:57:48,620 --> 01:57:51,160
The Wedding Pulav.

1850
01:57:51,290 --> 01:57:52,660
Come on, kiss..

1851
01:57:52,750 --> 01:57:54,120
Lambu, kiss him.

1852
01:57:54,410 --> 01:57:55,410
Come on.

1853
01:57:57,290 --> 01:57:58,370
Come on. - What is she doing?

1854
01:57:58,410 --> 01:58:00,370
What are you doing? Come on.

1855
01:58:00,620 --> 01:58:01,750
Hurry up.

1856
01:58:10,910 --> 01:58:12,040
Sweety. - Yeah.

1857
01:58:12,120 --> 01:58:13,870
The son's going for his honeymoon. - Yes.

1858
01:58:13,910 --> 01:58:15,620
What about the father?

1859
01:58:16,250 --> 01:58:17,870
You are just. - What?

1860
01:58:18,120 --> 01:58:19,870
Too much. - What?

1861
01:58:20,000 --> 01:58:21,790
Forget it. - Why?

1862
01:58:22,410 --> 01:58:24,540
Carry on then. - I am.

1863
01:58:26,500 --> 01:58:28,120
I am not doing it to you.

1864
01:58:28,750 --> 01:58:30,500
Did you two break up?

1865
01:58:31,000 --> 01:58:33,870
No, she said yes.

1866
01:58:35,410 --> 01:58:37,500
Play this song again.

1867
01:58:38,160 --> 01:58:39,370
Thanks, Jay.

1868
01:58:40,120 --> 01:58:41,790
This love story wouldn't be complete without you.

1869
01:58:42,910 --> 01:58:44,120
It's not complete yet.

1870
01:58:44,540 --> 01:58:45,870
